Description: This package contains functions for performing power and sample size calculations 
    for a variety of different study designs and outcomes. It is a companion to 
    the forthcoming book 'Power and Sample Size in R' (2025) by 
    Catherine M. Crespi, CRC Press/Chapman & Hall.
